 setiap harinya\",\"link\":\"#\",\"text2\":\"undefined\",\"title\":\"Keunggulan\",\"subtitle\":\"undefined\",\"social_repeater\":\"undefined\",\"id\":\"social-repeater-5caaa3bbc5dd8\",\"shortcode\":\"undefined\"},{\"icon_value\":\"fa-globe\",\"color\":\"#4caf50\",\"text\":\"Channel Telegram @cryptorizubot @profitrizubotIndonesian Telegram Group&#x2F; Group Telegram Indonesia @koinrizubot @diskusirizubotInternational Telegram Group&#x2F; Group TelegramInternasional @worldrizubot Facebook @rizubot main contact&#x2F; kontakutama @admrzb\",\"link\":\"#\",\"text2\":\"undefined\",\"title\":\"Social Media\",\"subtitle\":\"undefined\",\"social_repeater\":\"undefined\",\"id\":\"social-repeater-5caaa3bbbe0ce\",\"shortcode\":\"undefined\"}]\";s:21:\"hestia_features_title\";s:23:\"Project Review: Rizubot\";s:24:\"hestia_features_subtitle\";s:135:\"Rizubot merupakan salah satu uang digital yang berasal dari Indonesia , Rizubot ini sendiri baru berjalan sejak bulan April tahun 2018.\";s:17:\"hestia_about_hide\";b:0;s:17:\"hestia_shop_items\";i:5;s:16:\"hestia_shop_hide\";b:1;s:21:\"hestia_subscribe_hide\";b:0;s:18:\"hestia_ribbon_hide\";b:0;s:23:\"hestia_clients_bar_hide\";b:1;s:17:\"hestia_team_title\";s:12:\"Rizubot team\";s:20:\"hestia_team_subtitle\";s:29:\"Together We Can Be Successful\";s:18:\"hestia_ribbon_text\";s:28:\"Join to our Telegram Channel\";s:24:\"hestia_ribbon_button_url\";s:25:\"http://t.me/cryptorizubot\";s:25:\"hestia_testimonials_title\";s:14:\"Rizubot Dreams\";s:28:\"hestia_testimonials_subtitle\";s:52:\"Project Pengembangan dan Komunitas Rizubot Indonesia\";s:22:\"hestia_subscribe_title\";s:41:\"🏠️Visit to home page Rizubot 🖥️\";s:25:\"hestia_subscribe_subtitle\";s:19:\"http://rizubot.com/\";s:20:\"hestia_blog_subtitle\";s:9:\"News Info\";s:19:\"hestia_contact_hide\";b:0;s:20:\"hestia_contact_title\";s:19:\" Contact me 🚀️\";s:23:\"hestia_contact_subtitle\";s:71:\"More information for this blog. Please, email to afrizal@afrizal.web.id\";s:25:\"hestia_contac