emiliki Komunitas Yang Solid dan Kuat. Kami memiliki lebih dari 10.800 Holders di seluruh dunia dan semakin bertambah setiap harinya\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"#\\\",\\\"text2\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Keunggulan\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"social-repeater-5caaa3bbc5dd8\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"icon_value\\\":\\\"fa-globe\\\",\\\"color\\\":\\\"#4caf50\\\",\\\"text\\\":\\\"Channel Telegram @cryptorizubot @profitrizubotIndonesian Telegram Group&#x2F; Group Telegram Indonesia @koinrizubot @diskusirizubotInternational Telegram Group&#x2F; Group TelegramInternasional @worldrizubot Facebook @rizubot main contact&#x2F; kontakutama @admrzb\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"#\\\",\\\"text2\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Social Media\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"social-repeater-5caaa3bbbe0ce\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"}]\",\n        \"type\": \"theme_mod\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-04-08 08:54:55\"\n    },\n    \"orfeo::hestia_testimonials_content\": {\n        \"value\": \"[{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Curabitur nec sem vel sapien venenatis mattis non vitae augue. Nullam congue commodo lorem vitae facilisis. Suspendisse malesuada id turpis interdum dictum.\\\",\\\"link\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"text2\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"image_url\\\":\\\"https://blog.afrizalmy.com/wp-content/themes/zerif-lite/images/testimonial1.jpg\\\",\\\"title\\\":\\\"Dana Lorem\\\",\\\"subtitle\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"social_repeater\\\":\\\"undefined\\\",\\\"id\\\":\\\"social-repeater-5caaa3bb4f40a\\\",\\\"shortcode\\\":\\\"undefined\\\"},{\\\"text\\\":\\\"Cum sociis natoque penatibus et magnis dis parturient montes, nascetur ridiculus mus. Curabitur nec sem vel sapien venenatis mattis non vitae augue. Nullam congue commodo lorem vi