,'2019-04-08 09:30:22','2019-04-08 09:30:22',' ','','','publish','closed','closed','','83','','','2019-04-08 09:30:22','2019-04-08 09:30:22','',0,'https://blog.afrizalmy.com/2019/04/08/83/',2,'nav_menu_item','',0),(84,1,'2019-04-08 09:31:27','2019-04-08 09:31:27','<!-- wp:html -->\n<p>The website is done using the Wordpress&nbsp;and supports PWA (Progressive Web App) technology. The purpose of this website is to provide information to the general public about technology. <br />With this PWA technology, it is possible that this website will be easily crawled by search engines,<br />I have read an article because today for the web crawler search engine, the most understood machine is the Javascript language.<br />However, it is felt that when using SSR (Server Side Rendering) technology, my website still uses SPA (Single Page Application) and CSR (Client Side Rendering). But for the future I hope this website can be indexed by search engines with a satisfactory rating.</p>\n<p>With renewable technology it can be a selling price, but for this website it still needs improvement.<br />It takes a week for crawling by search engines with unique keywords.</p>\n<p>Thank you for visiting my dynamic website, hopefully getting useful knowledge.<br />I ask for help to review my website by filling out the form below.</p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->','About Me','','publish','closed','closed','','about-me','','','2019-04-11 12:13:06','2019-04-11 12:13:06','',0,'https://blog.afrizalmy.com/?page_id=84',0,'page','',0),(85,1,'2019-04-08 09:31:27','2019-04-08 09:31:27','{\n    \"nav_menus_created_posts\": {\n        \"value\": [\n            84\n        ],\n        \"type\": \"option\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-04-08 09:31:24\"\n    },\n    \"nav_menu_item[-7867625896776221000]\": {\n        \"value\": false,\n        \"type\": \"nav_menu_item\",\n        \"user_id\": 1,\n        \"date_modified_gmt\": \"2019-04-08 09:31:27\"\n    },\n    \"nav_menu_item[-8