nt Side Rendering). But for the future I hope this website can be indexed by search engines with a satisfactory rating.</p>\n<p>With renewable technology it can be a selling price, but for this website it still needs improvement.<br />It takes a week for crawling by search engines with unique keywords.</p>\n<p>Thank you for visiting my dynamic website, hopefully getting useful knowledge.<br />I ask for help to review my website by filling out the form below.</p>\n<!-- /wp:html -->','About Me','','inherit','closed','closed','','84-revision-v1','','','2019-04-11 12:12:58','2019-04-11 12:12:58','',84,'https://blog.afrizalmy.com/2019/04/11/84-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(115,1,'2019-04-11 13:00:27','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','Auto Draft','','auto-draft','open','open','','','','','2019-04-11 13:00:27','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://blog.afrizalmy.com/?p=115',0,'post','',0),(116,1,'2019-04-11 13:21:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','NextGEN Basic Thumbnails','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2019-04-11 13:21:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://blog.afrizalmy.com/?post_type=display_type&p=116',0,'display_type','',0),(117,1,'2019-04-11 13:21:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','NextGEN Basic Slideshow','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2019-04-11 13:21:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://blog.afrizalmy.com/?post_type=display_type&p=117',0,'display_type','',0),(118,1,'2019-04-11 13:21:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','NextGEN Basic ImageBrowser','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2019-04-11 13:21:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://blog.afrizalmy.com/?post_type=display_type&p=118',0,'display_type','',0),(119,1,'2019-04-11 13:21:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','NextGEN Basic SinglePic','','draft','closed','closed','','','','','2019-04-11 13:21:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','',0,'https://blog.afrizalmy.com/?post_type=display_type&p=119',0,'display_type','',0),(120,1,'2019-04-11 13:21:15','0000-00-00 00:00:00','','NextGEN Basic TagCloud','','draft','closed',